Package org.omg.dds.sub

Interface SubscriberListener

All Superinterfaces:
EventListener
All Known Subinterfaces:
DomainParticipantListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
DomainParticipantAdapter, SubscriberAdapter
public interface SubscriberListener extends EventListener
Since a Subscriber is a kind of Entity, it has the ability to have an associated listener. In this case, the associated listener must be of concrete type SubscriberListener.
